title: #92Noon! LaVelle/Florio/Greenway/Harris/Sendejo/Stefanski live
description: #92Noon returns to #Vikings training camp! LaVelle E. Neal III talks Twins, Mike Florio checks in, Chad Greenway hangs out at the perch, Super Bowl 50 champ Ryan Harris joins the show, Andrew Sendejo shares his insight from training camp and Vikings QB coach Kevin Stefanski talks about the quarterbacks!
